Source: https://pypi.org/project/pyLoRa/

How to Use: 
	 if you are running on an Arduino 
	 the LORA_CLIENT (https://github.com/rpsreal/LoRa_Ra-02_Arduino/blob/master/LORA_CLIENT.ino)
	 then start the LORA_SERVER.py (https://github.com/rpsreal/pySX127x/blob/master/LORA_SERVER.py) 
	 on Raspberry Pi. 
	 
Github (Arduino): https://github.com/rpsreal/LoRa_Ra-02_Arduino
Github (Pi) : https://github.com/rpsreal/pySX127x